<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وقال رحمه الله يصف الدنيا:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لَكِنَّ ذَا الإِيمَانِ يَعْلَمُ أَنَّ هَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ذَا كَالضَّلالِ وَكُلُّ هَذَا فَانِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>كَخَيَالِ طَيْفٍ مَا اسْتَتَمَّ زِيَارَةً<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>إِلا وَصُبْحُ رَحِيلِهِ بِأَذَانِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَسَحَابَةٍ طَلَعَتْ بِيَوْمٍ صَائِفٍ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَالظِّلُّ مَنْسُوخٌ بِقُرْبِ زَمَانِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَكَزَهْرَةٍ وَافَى الرَّبِيعُ بِحُسْنِهَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَوْ لامِعًا فَكِلاهُمَا إِخْوَانِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>أَوْ كَالسَّرَابِ يَلُوحُ لِلظَّمْآنِ فِي<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَسَطَ الْهَجِيرِ بِمُسْتَوَى الْقِيعَانِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أَوْ كَالأَمَانِي طَابَ مِنْهَا ذِكْرُهَا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>بِالْقَوْلِ وَاسْتِحْضَارُهَا بِجَنَانِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَهِيَ الْغُرُورُ رُؤُوسُ أَمْوَالِ الْمَفَا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>لِيسِ الأُولَى اتَّجَرُوا بِلا أَثْمَانِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>أَوْ كَالطَّعَامِ يَلَذُّ عِنْدَ مَسَاغِهِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لَكِنَّ عُقْبَاهُ كَمَا تَجِدَانِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>هَذَا هُوَ الْمَثَلُ الَّذِي ضَرَبَ الرَّسُو<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>لُ لَهَا وَذَا فِي غَايَةِ التِّبْيَانِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَإِذَا أَرَدْتَ تَرَى حَقِيقَتَهَا فَخُذْ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>مِنْهُ مِثَالاً وَاحِدًا ذَا شَانِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>أَدْخِلْ بِجَهْدِكَ أَصْبُعًا فِي الْيَمِّ وَانْـ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>